In recent news the rights of women all over the world are being tested. At this time it’s important for us women to stand together and show our strength. Speak up, be brave and know your worth. Be proud that you were #bornaGIRL

PS: This is an adapted version of an original song I’ve been working on for a while. I changed some lyrics and music for this release. This is just a Sneak Peek. (Full thing on FB)
